title: 3D.Live.Pool.Full
description:
Name: 3D Live Pool

Description: "If you want a fun, easy to use, and varied computer pool game, you must give this one a shot. 3D Live Pool has great sound, the balls roll just like real ones, and you can position your cue shot to hit at various places on the cue ball for different spins! Play against the computer or another player."

How To: Full Game. Just Unzip and play.
